data.description: Welcome home! This stunning home in Davison is sitting on a corner lot that's just under an half acre with a fully fenced in back yard. Home was completely repainted, new carpet and flooring throughout and offers high vaulted ceilings in the living room, formal dining area, main floor laundry plus a half bath and perfect office area right off the kitchen. Upstairs you'll find an large master on-suite featuring a large walk-in closet and jacuzzi tub, also 2 additional bedrooms plus another full bathroom! This home has a 10 panel circuit ready for a whole home generator. Shed in the back yard has electric. This home is a must see and will make the perfect home for you.
